# Refactoring Plan for Dashboard Views

## Goal Description
The goal is to refactor [DailyMeetingView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx) and [NextSprintPlanningView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/NextSprintPlanningView.tsx) to get better structured code. This will reduce the context size needed for AI to understand the files and will make future coding implementations easier and faster, without breaking any existing functionality. 

### Diagnosis (Code Smells Identified):
- **Monolithic Components**: [DailyMeetingView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx) is over 3,000 lines and contains multiple large sub-components ([PersonSingleView](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#809-1157), [HistoricalView](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#1166-1284), [CompareView](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#1294-1831), [DraggableTaskCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#514-703), [SyncTaskDropdown](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#713-793)).
- **Mixed Concerns**: It mixes complex data transformation logic (e.g., [computePersonMeetingData](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#115-229), webhook formatting) with UI rendering.
- **High Cognitive Load**: The sheer file size makes it hard for AI models (and humans) to quickly grok the context.

## Proposed Changes

We will apply the "Extract Method" and "Extract Class/Module" refactoring patterns to break down the monolithic files into cohesive, smaller modules.

### Component: Daily Meeting View
We will create a new directory `src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/` to house the extracted chunks.

#### [NEW] `src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/types.ts`
- Move shared types ([CategoryFilterKey](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#68-69), [PersonMeetingData](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#78-85), [TaskCategory](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#60-67), [TodoWebhookItem](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#348-362), [TodoWebhookPayload](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#363-375), etc.) here.

#### [NEW] `src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/utils.ts`
- Extract pure helper functions such as [getLatestMeetingNote](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#93-99), [hasActivityInSprint](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#100-114), [computePersonMeetingData](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#115-229), [getVisibleTaskCount](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#230-239), [priorityDotColor](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/NextSprintPlanningView.tsx#67-75), [statusBadge](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/NextSprintPlanningView.tsx#76-90), [formatStaleHours](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#264-271), [formatCorporateName](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#272-295), [formatTodoListForDM](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#296-347), [formatTodoListForWebhook](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#376-453), and [sendTodoListToWebhook](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#454-494).

#### [NEW] `src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/DraggableTaskCard.tsx`
- Extract the [DraggableTaskCard](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#514-703) component and its props interface.

#### [NEW] `src/components/dashboard/daily-meeting/SyncTaskDropdown.tsx`
- Extract the [SyncTaskDropdown](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/src/components/dashboard/DailyMeetingView.tsx#713-793) component.

